1. Target your app:
   <pre class="terminal">
   $ bosh target -e MY-ENV -d MY-DEPLOYMENT
   </pre>

1. Download and save the current BOSH manifest:
   <pre class="terminal">
   $ bosh -e MY-ENV -d MY-DEPLOYMENT manifest > MY-MANIFEST.yml
   </pre>

1. In your BOSH manifest, change the `disable_container_network_policy` value to `true`.

1. Redeploy your app using the edited BOSH manifest:
   <pre class="terminal">
   $ bosh -e MY-ENV -d cf deploy cf-deployment/cf-deployment.yml
   </pre>
